{
  "message": "fix(build): add CGO build tags to Dolt storage for cross-compilation\n\nThe Dolt embedded driver requires CGO (ICU regex, zstd). Without build\ntags, CGO_ENABLED=0 builds fail on all platforms. This adds //go:build cgo\nto all Dolt storage files and extracts the Dolt server detection in init.go\ninto CGO-gated wrapper files.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\nExecuted-By: beads/crew/emma\nRig: beads\nRole: crew",
